The paper deals with Interactive Machine Learning (IML) and focuses on developing safe IML algorithms. The paper discusses Bayesian optimization and active learning, which are both subfields of machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with exploration in deterministic Markov Decision Processes (MDP), which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses regularity assumptions, which are a key aspect of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses safety, which is a key aspect of software engineering (cs.SE).
